{"tid":232778,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"專家教洗冷氣機　半個鐘煥然一新","createTime":"2017-05-07T04:49:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T01:29:37.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fcbd8350a37d0b6f98681d6f7c6ff1e4cb6481ba","tid":232778,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T04:49:40.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>專家教洗冷氣機　半個鐘煥然一新<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/tech/art/20170506/20011886\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Ftech%2Fart%2F20170506%2F20011886&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=c177644f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Ftech%2Fart%2F20170506%2F20011886&h=9c56e23f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/tech/art/20170506/20011886</a></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170506/large/06fu401p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170506%2Flarge%2F06fu401p.jpg&h=cf4d65a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夏天到！發覺封塵了整個冬季的冷氣機唔多涼？又是洗冷氣機的時候，今次找來專業冷氣技工，示範正確的洗機方法，30分鐘搞掂。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170506/large/06fu402p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170506%2Flarge%2F06fu402p.jpg&h=f6c05964&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n傑師傅洗冷氣機的經驗十分豐富，二十多年前由學徒做起，一直維修和清洗冷氣機。「好多人所說的『洗冷氣』，大多意指在五金舖買的罐裝清潔劑，洗洗前方的凍Coil（蒸發器盤管）了事；其實正式洗機，可是要連機身內的塵垢，以至後方的散熱Coil（冷凝器盤管）都要一併清洗。」傑師傅不時都有上門清洗家庭式冷氣機，以及商舖用的大型冷氣機，「洗冷氣機由拆機開始，首要當然是關上電錶總掣，再拆電線及機殼，最後將冷氣機卸下來清潔。不過絕不建議大家跟着做，因當中涉及220V電力裝置，所以必須由領有冷氣技工牌照的師傅清洗。」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170506/large/06fu404p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170506%2Flarge%2F06fu404p.jpg&h=85da20ee&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n清潔前，先看看用了5年的冷氣機是甚麼狀態，前方凍Coil非常骯髒，底盤已出現銹迹及青苔，摩打中軸更完全生銹，而一直未能清潔的散熱Coil骯髒程度更甚，會直接影響冷氣機的效能。「據悉這部冷氣機自安裝以來從未經過專業清洗，所以銹迹問題頗嚴重，大概再用上一年左右，可能就要換機了，因為摩打中軸完全生銹，有可能在使用中斷開來。其實建議一般家用機，每隔上一至兩年，都要找專業師傅清洗，可以延長冷氣機的壽命。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170506/large/06fu408p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170506%2Flarge%2F06fu408p.jpg&h=63eed3fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n清洗工作馬上開始，先來是為浴室蓋上防水墊，因為洗冷氣機的藥水有極強腐蝕性，另冷氣機的摩打及壓縮機位置，都要用膠布或毛巾蓋上，以防入水致弄壞。如果你也將要找師傅「洗冷氣」，從這幾個步驟可看出他們的細心程度，傑師傅指：「洗機當然要用高壓水槍，與一般家庭式手動水槍最大分別是電泵式水槍，水壓可達20-30Bar，直接射在皮膚表面，都可導致脫皮，所以絕不建議大家使用。」洗機第一步，是用高壓水槍噴勻全機，去除大型塵粒，再來是落洗機藥水，雖然名字都是「Coil水」，但比一般在五金舖買到的來得更強力及腐蝕性較高，「凍Coil及散熱Coil都要噴灑，基本一噴完就要清洗，否則有可能弄壞機件！」洗機過程大約30分鐘，舊機隨即變得一塵不染。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170506/large/06fu409p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170506%2Flarge%2F06fu409p.jpg&h=7495c7b9&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"87ab4c8b298e278fc45900fee7b094ba5cb16992","tid":232778,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T04:51:37.000Z","msg":"『洗冷氣』時經常會遇到一些需另外收費的事項，一直令大家深感疑惑，就例如「加雪種」吧！傑師傅教路：「正常是不用入雪種，若果漏雪種，就須拿回工場焊接，再抽真空後才可追加雪種，在家中是做不來的，如果有師傅對你說幫你在家中加雪種，有可能是巧立名目收錢。另外，冷氣機因生銹而需要塗防銹油，這方面亦應注意，因為修理前必須經打磨工序，再塗防銹油才能起作用，直接將油塗在生銹位置，到最後都會脫落下來，效用不大。一般窗口式冷氣機（1-2匹）的清洗費用約為$500至$700，掛牆式分體機（1-2匹）則大約$700至$1,000。最後清潔後謹記要試開一次，看是否運作正常，才算完成整個洗冷氣機工序。」"},{"pid":"57d04455f344cb11e13a3572e0468ddfc6d1c906","tid":232778,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T04:52:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/07/125239_4a67dd054876d1d7987e29f955adebad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F07%2F125239_4a67dd054876d1d7987e29f955adebad.jpg&h=9ac26c6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p71h911.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp71h911.jpg&h=448bcf7c&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"e1fb6addbf0386f0f66f460dbbf423508873d381","tid":232778,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T05:46:55.000Z","msg":"咁撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1acdb39aa814c4fbf28ddd5401c7ad28d0791c6","tid":232778,"uid":101028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T07:55:06.000Z","msg":"平既一部都係2-3k, 1-2年洗一次都幾密 唔多抵"},{"pid":"0085bbaee628da5b79f2cd1c894e500a021f6e80","tid":232778,"uid":70832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T07:59:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平既一部都係2-3k, 1-2年洗一次都幾密 唔多抵</blockquote><br />\n二三千。。。？ <br />\n邊度有咁平既冷氣機😮"},{"pid":"c185a96bd93a646ba040cb015c5569e17822cb41","tid":232778,"uid":101028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T09:15:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平既一部都係2-3k, 1-2年洗一次都幾密 唔多抵</blockquote><br />\n二三千。。。？ <br />\n邊度有咁平既冷氣機😮</blockquote><br />\n一匹係可以咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nGoogle 冷氣機》<a href=\"http://price.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprice.com&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=86d1eab6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">price.com</a>"},{"pid":"784ef86ad88f0940e6b9dcb4c7b11e5614d7cb56","tid":232778,"uid":101028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":